KlikFlex, one of the worldâ€™s leading manufacturers and installers of modular and multifunctional sports flooring surfaces, has completed the implementation of several projects regardless of the hard times for the construction industry brought about by the COVID-19 virus and the restrictions governments have put in place to curb its spread. The company delivered a multipurpose sports surfaces in a timely manner for the Royal Island Resort and Spa located in Baa Atoll, an administrative division of the Republic of Maldives. The project measured approximately 1200m2 featuring a futsal court, a badminton court, a tennis court, and a half basketball court.   